      "description": "## v0.1.6\n\n### Fixes\n\n- Fixed `lark-cli` command resolution on Windows, including common npm, nvm-windows, and Node.js installation paths.\n- Fixed Windows `.cmd` / `.bat` execution handling for plugin sync and pre-push sync.\n- Fixed pre-push helper installation/update so the new `lark-cli-command.mjs` helper is included.\n- Avoid injecting Windows-only fallback paths into macOS/Linux `PATH`.\n- Added cross-platform tests for `lark-cli` command resolution and pre-push Windows compatibility.",
