      "author": "wanghuan9",
      "description": "## Fixes\r\n\r\n- Fixed precise sync state refresh so the local cache is not updated before the remote document content is confirmed visible.\r\n- Fixed a case where adding text to a heading and then deleting it could be incorrectly treated as already synced.\r\n- Fixed remote block mapping rebuild when the local sync cache is missing, `units` is empty, or stored mappings become invalid.\r\n- Improved skipped-state validation for `pre-push` and automatic sync: cached matches now verify remote content and repair from the real remote state when needed.\r\n- Improved state refresh after complex precise updates, reducing cases where later syncs keep falling back to full overwrite.",
